reviews.review_text: Rise and Fall..Rise and Fall Nice sound here but not on par with most 85' SBDs..The Let it Grow is smoking!! Not a big Touch of Grey fan so that hurts the start of the 2nd set for me..but the Hell in a Bucket>Terrapin makes up for it!! smooth sailing to U.S. Blues..so please>GIVE IT A WHIRL>Forever Grateful>Forever Dead!!!!!!
